━━━ HISTORICAL REFERENCE — SIMILAR CAPAs ━━━
{% if similar_capas %}
The following past CAPAs at {{ org_name }} share context with this one. Reference them where relevant:
{% for c in similar_capas %}
- [{{ c.capa_id }}] {{ c.title }} (site {{ c.site_id }}, group {{ c.group_id }})
  Root cause: {{ c.root_cause_summary }}
  Action taken: {{ c.action_summary[:200] }}
  Outcome: {{ c.effectiveness_result or "Unknown" }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
No similar historical CAPAs found.
{% endif %}

━━━ WHAT "STRONG" LOOKS LIKE — EFFECTIVE PAST ACTIONS ━━━
{% if effective_actions %}
These past actions received a "Strong" rating and passed effectiveness checks:
{% for a in effective_actions %}
- [{{ a.action_type }}] {{ (a.description or "")[:200] }}
  Evidence required: {{ a.evidence_required }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
No strong historical actions available for reference.
{% endif %}

━━━ RELEVANT SOPs ━━━
{% if relevant_sops %}
{% for s in relevant_sops %}
- {{ s.title }}: {{ s.excerpt[:300] }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
No relevant SOPs retrieved.
{% endif %}

━━━ REGULATORY CONTEXT ━━━
{% if regulatory_context %}
{% for r in regulatory_context %}
- {{ r.title }}: {{ r.excerpt[:300] }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
No regulatory context retrieved.
{% endif %}

━━━ ENTERPRISE CONTEXT (employees) ━━━
{% if enterprise_context %}
{% for result in enterprise_context %}
{% for row in result.rows[:10] %}
- {{ row }}
{% endfor %}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
No enterprise context available.
{% endif %}
